title: Team ELIM LF Subs for Top/Mid
body:
Team ELIM is currently looking for a few players to sub in for top and mid for practice in the coming weeks.
Benefits include competitive experience and an the opportunity to try out for the main roster if you do well.

For more information - 
Msg "ELIM thePinch" ingame; or 
Email "charliewraith@outlook.com" 

Thanks
